title: Spectator Out Loud: Jacob Rees-Mogg, Julian Jessop and Melanie McDonagh
description:
On this week's podcast: former Business Secretary Jacob Rees-Mogg tells us why it's good to back on the back benches (01:00), Julian Jessop reflects on his part in Liz Truss's downfall (06:41), and Melanie McDonagh reads her Notes on... candles (12:57).Â 

Produced and presented by Oscar Edmondson.
